  "detailed_description": "In 2035 Insurgents Take over a middle eastern country and launch nuclear strikes on the Global Alliance Forces in the nearby countries.<br />\r\nYou are dispatched to locate and destroy the remaining missiles before they strike again.<br />\r\nYou face Different enemies in the deserts of the middle east.<br />\r\nThis Game is an homage to the old third person shooters of the 90s.<br />\r\nThe Game is made with Unreal Engine 4, It is a Military third person shooter where you fight intelligent AI that can take cover when shot at, you can pickup weapons dropped by the killed enemies, you can carry 3 weapons.<br />\r\nIn the game you should complete missions like locating and destroying weapon caches and Missiles.",
  "about_the_game": "In 2035 Insurgents Take over a middle eastern country and launch nuclear strikes on the Global Alliance Forces in the nearby countries.<br />\r\nYou are dispatched to locate and destroy the remaining missiles before they strike again.<br />\r\nYou face Different enemies in the deserts of the middle east.<br />\r\nThis Game is an homage to the old third person shooters of the 90s.<br />\r\nThe Game is made with Unreal Engine 4, It is a Military third person shooter where you fight intelligent AI that can take cover when shot at, you can pickup weapons dropped by the killed enemies, you can carry 3 weapons.<br />\r\nIn the game you should complete missions like locating and destroying weapon caches and Missiles.",
